      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IExtractStage<TSource>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IExtractStage-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Represents the extractor stage of a fluent ETL pipeline for items of type\n<code class=\"typeparamref\">TSource</code>. Call one of the <code>Transform</code> overloads to append a\ntransformer, or one of the <code>Load</code> overloads to terminate the chain with a loader.</p>\n"
    },
