      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IPipeline.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A terminated, runnable ETL pipeline. Obtained from an <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IExtractStage%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> or\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.ITransformStage%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> <code>Load</code> overload.</p>\n"
