      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IPipelineWithLoadProgress-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IPipeline\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> whose loader supports progress reporting. Call\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IPipelineWithLoadProgress%601.WithProgress(System.IProgress%7b%600%7d)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to supply an <xref href=\"System.IProgress%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> sink that will be\nforwarded to the loader's <code>LoadAsync</code> overload when the pipeline runs.</p>\n"
